title: The Sims 3 Complete
description:
This is the total sims 3 game, all the expansions are included into it.

you can see all the expansions above here.

How to install:
just install the base game first, you can use the CD-Key.txt for the game to install it.

after that, you can choose which expansions you want to install and you also can use the CD-Key.txt from every expansion to activate.

After you installed all the expansions you wanted, you place the three files from the folder Crack to 

C:Program Files(x86)electronic ArtsThe Sims 3The Sims 3GameBin and replace the files.

after that, you can play the game.
